_001.html</code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"毫無意義即係冇干預到啦<br />\n咁咪繼續制裁"},{"pid":"5475cd7a97be6ecccec89791ec2ec9f5f2915a08","tid":2145281,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"一世留係大灣區用現金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bca79933a138e6212977a244edcb50b6c76447","tid":2145281,"uid":129877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T04:07:23.000Z","msg":"哭泣聲絕無意義<br />\n它不會扭轉侵侵的心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d30c3228cc6fa4d948deb882a1f6495b18593a","tid":2145281,"uid":326712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"02162c89f808f9ff387b3e877d941d6b891ac772","tid":2145281,"uid":284630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:54:12.000Z","msg":"其實我信果班狗官係為權賣港<br />\n俾美帝制裁佢地真係冇乜所謂<br />\n肥婆華肯撚定係為錢, 依家講不出聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T04:08:28.000Z","msg":"諗住同老公搞好盤生意<br />\n入左政府做打尖搞埋上市<br />\n點知而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2ec3e0331a1d110035a5f53270759206a8f796","tid":2145281,"uid":273294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b0f39751e5ca5af86c8b1290ebd0e572f9ce29e","tid":2145281,"uid":321157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5afea656055598af196ca4784de984774dd8194d","tid":2145281,"uid":273294,"like":94,"dislike":57,"score":37,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bumkex6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBumkex6.png&h=d530c894&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T04:02:59.000Z","msg":"波叔係咪你呀波叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T04:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets